Author: Mahesh Divakaran [aut, cre] (ORCID:
    <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3488-0857>)
Maintainer: Mahesh Divakaran <imaheshdivakaran@gmail.com>
Description: Provides high-performance read/write capabilities for clinical
    data formats used in pharmaceutical regulatory submissions. Supports SAS
    Transport (XPT v5 and v8), SAS7BDAT, Excel (xlsx), and CSV formats with
    comprehensive metadata management including variable labels, SAS format
    strings (e.g. DATE9., $CHAR200.), variable byte-length control, and
    automatic column-name sanitisation for XPT compliance. Includes a
    spec-driven workflow for applying variable metadata from a specification
    sheet, and a CDISC validation layer for FDA/PMDA eCTD submissions
    following SDTM and ADaM standards. Does not depend on 'haven' or
    'xportr'.
